This repo was generated from [simple-modern-pnpm](https://github.com/jlevy/simple-modern-pnpm), an agent-friendly template for a modern model repo in TypeScript using pnpm.

## Bootstrap

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm check
```

If you created this repo in a scratch directory before `git init`, run:

```bash
git init -b main
pnpm prepare
```

## Template Updates

Keep `.copier-answers.yml` committed. To pull upstream template updates:

```bash
uvx copier update
pnpm install
pnpm check
```

